# Password Policy

## Purpose
To ensure all users create and maintain strong passwords to protect sensitive data.

## Password Requirements
- Passwords must be at least 12 characters.
- Must include a mix of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols.
- Passwords should be changed every 90 days.
- Use multi-factor authentication for sensitive accounts.

## Consequences of Non-Compliance
Failure to follow this policy will result in account suspension and potential disciplinary action.
